<http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/hydro/dynamic/seasonal-rainfall.htm>
3. Jelinek T, Behrens R, Bisoffi Z, Bjorkmann A, Andersen P, Blaxhult A, et
al. Recent cases of falciparum malaria imported to Europe from Goa, India,
December 2006-January 2007. Euro Surveill 2007; 12(1): E070111.1. Available
