[The Eurosurveillance publication sums up the problem of malaria in Goa.
ProMED-mail posted data from the Ministry of Health, New Delhi showing an
increase in cases during the 1st half of 2007 (Malaria - India (Goa,
Rajastan) 20070716.2287). The data for the 2nd half of 2007 have not yet
been made publicly available. - Mod.EP

Goa on the west coast and Kerala in south western India can be located on
the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at
<http://healthmap.org/promed?v=22.9,79.6,5>. - CopyEd.MJ]
